# {{ profile.metadata.name }} — {{ role_display_name }} Onboarding Guide

Welcome to **{{ profile.metadata.name }}**! This guide will help you set up Cursor with the right permissions and context for your role.

## Quick Setup

1. **Clone the repository**:
   ```bash
   git clone {{ profile.metadata.repo_url or '<repo-url>' }}
   cd {{ profile.metadata.name | lower | replace(' ', '-') }}
   ```

2. **Install Product Builders CLI** (if not already installed):
   ```bash
   pip install product-builders
   ```

3. **Set up your Cursor environment**:
   ```bash
   product-builders setup --name "{{ profile.metadata.name }}" --role {{ role }}
   ```

   This command generates:
   - `.cursor/rules/` — AI rules tailored to your role
   - `.cursor/hooks.json` — Smart guardrails (Layer 2)
   - `.cursor/cli.json` — Filesystem permissions (Layer 3)

